{"tid":2242210,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，意大利大餐(4 courses)","createTime":"2020-10-14T00:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:15:37.000Z","uid":93141,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7c435f55a3dca70d247ad79de49bfeb8743a762e","tid":2242210,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2u3sFD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2u3sFD6.jpg&h=efd25446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCaprese: 番茄，mozzarella，羅勒，胡椒，鹽，橄欖油，意大利黑醋<br />\n<br />\n番茄同mozzarella切開後，加埋羅勒梅花間竹<br />\n撒上胡椒，鹽，淋上橄欖油同黑醋就搞掂<br />\n<br />\nTapenade：黑橄欖，青橄欖，酸豆，蒜頭，檸檬皮，風乾番茄，鯷魚，胡椒，鹽，橄欖油<br />\n<br />\n切碎所有材料，加入調味<br />\n配上烤過既薄切麵包就搞掂<br />\n<br />\nProsciutto e Melone：意大利風乾火腿，哈密瓜，火箭菜，胡椒，意大利黑醋<br />\n<br />\n用火腿將哈密瓜包起<br />\n配上火箭菜，撒上胡椒粉，淋上黑醋就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n迷迭香炆雞：雞腿，長辣椒對半切，迷迭香，原粒蒜頭，白酒，胡椒，鹽<br />\n<br />\n胡椒，鹽醃雞肉，中火煎到雞肉表面金黃，攞起備用<br />\n同pan大火爆香紅蔥頭，蒜頭，辣椒<br />\n加迷迭香翻炒，出香味後落白酒沖走煲底梅納反應物<br />\n落雞肉，將其他材料擺雞肉上面，加蓋轉細火煮25-30分鐘<br />\n攞起雞肉擺碟，再用大火收汁，過篩後淋返上雞肉就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ebf8958f90ca895c1dca2e3f5ff5a2af59afb5","tid":2242210,"uid":93141,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:30:23.000Z","msg":"Rare image of 樓主食野毫冇儀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvu0gcZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdvu0gcZ.jpg&h=dc6ee72d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf766783b907666df56ecbf10193410ef864042","tid":2242210,"uid":113525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"日日做甜品真開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b8489b367d3b387dc7e762bfdb07ef74b7b729